'''阿根廷南方航空2553號班機空難'''是[[阿根廷南方航空|阿根廷南方航空]]（Austral Líneas Aéreas）一班的來回[[波萨达斯|波萨达斯]][[何塞·德·聖馬丁將軍機場|何塞·德·聖馬丁將軍機場]]至[[布宜諾斯艾利斯|布宜諾斯艾利斯]][[豪尔赫·纽伯里机场|豪尔赫·纽伯里机场]]的定期航班，1997年10月10日<ref name="Catástrofe aérea: hubo 73 muertos">{{cite news|title= Catástrofe aérea: hubo 73 muertos|first= Roberto|last= Solans|newspaper= [[La_Nación|La Nación]]|date= 1997-10-12|language= es|trans_title= Air disaster: 73 dead|url= http://www.lanacion.com.ar/78605-catastrofe-aerea-hubo-73-muertos|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140315135133/http://www.lanacion.com.ar/78605-catastrofe-aerea-hubo-73-muertos|archivedate= 2014-03-15|deadurl= no}}</ref><ref name="AviationSafety">{{cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19971010-0|title=ASN Aircraft accident McDonnell Douglas DC-9-32 LV-WEG Nuevo Berlin|accessdate=2011-05-26|archive-date=2011-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011094044/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19971010-0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Catástrofe aérea: hubo 73 muertos" /><ref name="Scary">{{cite news|title= Imágenes del espanto en Nuevo Berlín|url= http://www.lanacion.com.ar/nota.asp?nota_id=78606|newspaper= [[La_Nación|La Nación]]|date= 1997-10-12|accessdate=2011-05-19|language= es|trans_title= Scary pictures at Nuevo Berlín|archive-date= 2016-08-24|archive-url= https://archive.today/20160824202920/http://www.lanacion.com.ar/78606-imagenes-del-espanto-en-nuevo-berlin|dead-url= no}}</ref>，一架[[道格拉斯DC-9|道格拉斯DC-9]][[客機|客機]]墜毀於[[新柏林_(乌拉圭)|新柏林市]]，造成74名乘客死亡<ref name="AviationSafety"/><ref name="Timeline: Worst air accidents in Argentina">{{cite news|title= Timeline: Worst air accidents in Argentina|newspaper= [[Buenos_Aires_Herald|Buenos Aires Herald]]|date=2011-05-19|url= http://www.buenosairesherald.com/article/67564/timeline-worst-air-accidents-in-argentina|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140315141337/http://www.buenosairesherald.com/article/67564/timeline-worst-air-accidents-in-argentina|archivedate= 2014-03-15|deadurl= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=El piloto no debió entrar en la tormenta|url=http://www.lanacion.com.ar/nota.asp?nota_id=78669|newspaper=[[La_Nación|La Nación]]|date=1997-10-13|accessdate=2011-05-04|language=es|trans_title=The pilot should had not entered into the storm|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713131937/https://www.lanacion.com.ar/sociedad/el-piloto-no-debio-entrar-en-la-tormenta-nid78669|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==飛機==
失事客機是一架編號為LV-WEG的[[道格拉斯DC-9|麥道DC-9-32]]，<ref name="AviationSafety"/><ref name="Catástrofe aérea: hubo 73 muertos"/><ref name="FI">{{cite journal|title=Storm may be to blame for Austral DC-9 crash|journal=[[Flight_International|Flight International]]|pages=11|format=pdf|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1997/1997%20-%202751.html|date=1997-10-22{{spaced ndash}}1997-10-28|accessdate=2011-04-29}}</ref>於1969年首飛，<ref name="AviationSafety"/>事發時機齡28年，原先服役于[[西班牙國家航空|西班牙國家航空]]，編號為EC-BQT。

==原因==
據阿根廷空軍和烏拉圭空軍的調查顯示，飛機在通過[[積雨雲|積雨雲]]時，[[皮托管|皮托管]]的凍結引發了空速表數據不准，導致機師操作失誤。<ref name="AviationSafety"/>

